769
01:06:53,240 --> 01:06:58,519
That means, if you're done, sickness unto death, Christianity produces this despair.

770
01:06:58,519 --> 01:07:00,919
The Greeks and the Buddhists don't have it.

771
01:07:00,919 --> 01:07:16,199
