772
01:07:16,200 --> 01:07:34,999
And anybody raised in this culture, it isn't in our DNA, anybody raised in our culture with our language, with our practices, with our books and movies and millions of paintings of the biblical stories and so forth, can't help but have this kind of self.

773
01:07:35,479 --> 01:07:44,759
